<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l24">wır 
<add><ab facs="#facs_138_line_1585819527728_151">Jn </ab></add> ın <expan>v<ex>er</ex>dechtnuſſ</expan> haben <expan>ſüll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> daʒ er mıt <expan>hannſ<ex>en</ex></expan> von Mılcʒ . der </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_138_r2l25">doch für ſıch vnd dıe <expan>ſeine<ex>n</ex></expan> mıt vns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſünet</expan> ſey . ettwenn <expan>gerıtte<ex>n</ex></expan> ſey etc </ab>
